{"tid":2286641,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"遇拜登我即刻變大個","createTime":"2020-11-15T07:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T04:10:34.000Z","uid":139613,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f92474afb7fad16973e491ab1f9eb525350a997","tid":2286641,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"示威紛爭繼續高企 遇武肺戰意又再起<br />\n搣走口罩 憑熱血 免疫必勝利<br />\n共匪滲透煽動反美 內鬥會鬥到廿六世紀<br />\n克警相信 盲目撐 佢定必勝利<br />\n<br />\n話就話 賓州想擺動<br />\n內華達數夠票哪怕會甩飛<br />\n賣力落 北卡都有用<br />\n喬治亞 密歇根 仍舊會部署準備<br />\n<br />\n遇拜燈我即刻變大個<br />\n投向侵侵痛快得多<br />\n爭德州我就有火<br />\n儘快儘快辨勝負 問邊家選票多<br />\n<br />\n告上終審 梗冇做錯<br />\n原告主控法官都顧忌我<br />\n我但求贏多屆<br />\n侵~對~燈！"},{"pid":"58cb57336fe05b1013d9913ea24d2500a050a414","tid":2286641,"uid":177955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"迎接光輝歲月"},{"pid":"05d1e962598344f6af8ddef051d82cbdbc6e4eac","tid":2286641,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老味頭四隻字已經唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50795de743e107c39ecfa1c9d35dd53a8eb154d","tid":2286641,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05d1e962598344f6af8ddef051d82cbdbc6e4eac","tid":2286641,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老味頭四隻字已經唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"唔好沖出嚟柒"},{"pid":"7eaa9cbf9d8a754ee7b5c943de2364c7c460006d","tid":2286641,"uid":61498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"示喂紛震"},{"pid":"3ea48aed92f74a46f3e0452af5c59f4c589a7192","tid":2286641,"uid":141203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05d1e962598344f6af8ddef051d82cbdbc6e4eac","tid":2286641,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老味頭